notes.title: Data Availability
notes.p: The data cannot be made publicly available because it contains links between participant names and ID numbers, which was necessary for the purpose of conducting longitudinal network analyses. Requests for data accession may be directed to the IRB at the University of Michigan: RB HEALTH SCIENCES AND BEHAVIORAL SCIENCES, 2800 Plymouth Road, Bldg. 520, Rm. 1169, Ann Arbor, MI 48109-2800, Phone: (734) 936-0933, Fax: (734) 936-1852, irbhsbs@umich.edu.
